title: Watch Out For Soaring Oil Prices
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: Global oil output hit a record last month, and the IEA sees continued increases in oil production. On the other hand, bond king Jeffrey Gundlach sees oil heading as high $80 or $90 a barrel. Who’s right? A story the media is paying little attention to seems to indicate that, overall, oil market risk is rising. Learn more about your ad choices. Visit megaphone.fm/adchoices
